metadata.name: Murakami's Gift
metadata.description:
There is nothing more inspiring than art that can give hope, transform, evolve, transcend, liberate and that is exactly what Murakami Flowers mean to me. That's the reason why I chose to create this piece in honor of a legendary artist and inspiration, Takashi Murakami.

❤️ 🧡 💛 💚 💙 💜 🖤

⏳ 2 Days  
🖼️ 108 Slides  
📚 10 Layers

❤️ 🧡 💛 💚 💙 💜 🖤
